### 1. LINKEDIN (B2B - Fleet Managers & Decision Makers)

**Prompt 1A – Corporate Fleet Wrap (Landscape 1200x627)**
> *Professional LinkedIn banner image for a printing company. A serious, well-dressed fleet manager standing confidently next to a fleet of three branded delivery vans in an industrial depot. The vans have a crisp, clean corporate wrap with bold logo and contact details. The lighting is cool and professional, like a corporate headshot setting. Emphasize the scale of the job and the precision of the vinyl application. No text overlay, clean composition, high-end B2B aesthetic, photorealistic, 8k resolution.*

**Prompt 1B – Office Window Branding (Square 1080x1080)**
> *A modern corporate office building entrance with large glass doors and windows featuring high-quality frosted window printing. The design includes the company logo, elegant geometric patterns, and the words "Welcome" in crisp typography. A business professional in a suit is walking through the door. Bright daylight, clean city surroundings. Focus on the precision of the cut vinyl and the professional appearance. Photorealistic, commercial architecture photography style, high fidelity.*

**Prompt 1C – Before & After Document Upgrade (Landscape 1200x627)**
> *Split-screen image for a printing company LinkedIn post. Left side: a messy, outdated pile of dull, faded business cards and brochures on a cluttered desk. Right side: the same business's materials transformed—vibrant, glossy, premium brochures, thick matte business cards with spot UV gloss, and a sleek presentation folder. A hand is pointing from the 'before' to the 'after'. Professional office background. High contrast, sharp details, corporate marketing style.*

