### 2. GOOGLE MY BUSINESS (Local SEO - "Near Me" Searches)

**Prompt 2A – Local Shop Window Print (Square 1200x900)**
> *A welcoming, friendly image for a local business Google profile. A wide shot of a small local bakery with beautiful frosted window printing displaying their logo, opening hours, and a "Fresh Bread" graphic. A smiling employee is waving from inside. Warm, golden-hour sunlight hitting the glass. The focus is on how the window print makes the small shop look premium and inviting. Community-focused, welcoming vibe, photorealistic, high detail.*

**Prompt 2B – Large Gateboard Installation (Square 1200x900)**
> *A large outdoor gateboard banner being professionally installed on a busy high street. Two installers in high-visibility vests are securing the banner onto a metal frame. The banner features bold, colorful advertising for a local event. Pedestrians are walking by in the background. Focus on the size and impact of the banner. Bright daytime lighting, clear blue sky. Commercial photography style, sharp focus.*

**Prompt 2C – Vehicle Wrap Being Applied (Square 1200x900)**
> *Close-up action shot of a printing company technician carefully applying a vibrant vinyl vehicle wrap to the side of a white van. The technician is using a squeegee and heat gun. The wrap features a colorful geometric abstract design. The van is in a clean, well-lit workshop garage. Focus on the texture of the vinyl and the detailed application process. Trust-building, behind-the-scenes feel. Photorealistic.*

