### 3. INSTAGRAM (Visual Portfolio - "Wow" Factor)

**Prompt 3A – Full Vehicle Wrap Reveal (Square 1080x1080)**
> *Instagram square image for a printing company. A stunning, fully wrapped sports car or delivery van with a vibrant, eye-catching custom design featuring neon gradients and bold typography. The vehicle is parked in front of a modern graffiti wall in an urban setting. The sun is setting, creating dramatic reflections on the glossy vinyl. High contrast, punchy colors, mobile-first composition, 8k, photorealistic, social media advertising style.*

**Prompt 3B – Door & Window "Ghost" Effect (Square 1080x1080)**
> *Instagram-worthy close-up shot of a glass storefront door with a stunning "Contra Vision" perforated window print. From the outside, it shows a massive, colorful product advertisement, but you can faintly see a mannequin inside the shop. The lighting creates a beautiful reflection of the city skyline on the glass. Minimalist, artistic, high-end aesthetic. Crisp details, shallow depth of field.*

**Prompt 3C – Flat Lay of Print Samples (Square 1080x1080)**
> *Aesthetically pleasing overhead flat-lay Instagram photo. High-quality printed items spread out on a white marble table: thick matte business cards, glossy brochures, a metallic foil-stamped invitation, and a roll of vinyl wrap sample swatches. Next to them are a coffee cup, a succulent plant, and a pair of sunglasses. Bright, airy lighting, pastel and neutral color palette. Minimalist, modern, influencer-style photography.*

