### 4. FACEBOOK (Community & Special Offers)

**Prompt 4A – "Free Quote" Offer Ad (Landscape 1200x628)**
> *Facebook feed ad image for a printing company. The main visual is a captivating shot of a massive, colorful building wrap (like a scaffolding banner) on a construction site, showing the scale of the project. In the bottom right corner, there is a small, clean white text box that says "FREE Quote - Click Here." The overall color palette is vibrant teal and orange to create high contrast. Design optimized for mobile scrolling. Professional, trustworthy, high fidelity.*

**Prompt 4B – Local Community Partnership (Landscape 1200x628)**
> *A warm, community-focused Facebook post image. A local restaurant owner is shaking hands with a Rest Ink team member outside the restaurant. The restaurant has beautiful new custom-printed menus displayed on an outdoor stand and elegant window lettering. The background shows a cozy street with fairy lights. Sunset lighting, warm color tones. This image tells a story of local partnership and quality work. Photorealistic, candid photography style.*

**Prompt 4C – Behind the Scenes Team Photo (Square 1080x1080)**
> *A cheerful, energetic team photo of the printing company staff standing in front of a large format printer in their workshop. They are holding up a freshly printed, colorful banner. High-fiving, smiling, looking proud of their work. Clean, modern workshop environment with bright LED lighting. Focus on the team spirit and professionalism. Humanizes the brand. Bright, crisp, social media friendly.*

