### 5. TWITTER / X (Quick Engagement & Bites)

**Prompt 5A – Extreme Before & After (Landscape 1200x675)**
> *Twitter image for maximum engagement. Extreme split-screen. Left side: a beat-up, faded, dirty old van with peeling decals parked in a junkyard. Right side: the exact same model van completely transformed with a stunning, vibrant, futuristic cyberpunk vehicle wrap in neon pink and blue. The contrast must be shocking and dramatic. High contrast, bold colors, viral-style content. Photorealistic.*

**Prompt 5B – Quote Graphic with Image (Landscape 1200x675)**
> *A motivational quote-style image for Twitter. Background shows a massive, eye-catching billboard/banner being printed in a workshop. Overlaid on the image in large, clean white text: "Your Brand. Our Canvas. Rest Ink." The typography is bold and modern, positioned in the bottom third of the image. No clutter. Professional, inspiring, high-impact visual. Dark background with vibrant colorful print emerging from the printer.*

