### 6. PINTEREST (Visual Search - Evergreen Traffic)

**Prompt 6A – Design Inspiration Collage (Tall 1000x1500)**
> *Highly stylized, artistic vertical Pinterest pin. A top-down flat lay of various vinyl wrap swatches (matte black, gloss white, metallic silver, bright orange, and carbon fiber) scattered next to a laptop showing a vehicle wrap design on screen. A coffee cup, a roll of measuring tape, and a color palette swatch book are in the shot. Minimalist, modern, inspirational aesthetic for designers and business owners. Bright natural lighting, clean composition, lifestyle photography.*

**Prompt 6B – Brand Transformation Step-by-Step (Tall 1000x1500)**
> *Vertical Pinterest infographic-style image. Three small images stacked vertically: Top: A plain white van. Middle: A technician applying the wrap. Bottom: The fully wrapped van looking spectacular. Overlaid on the right side is a small vertical text label: "3 Steps to a Branded Fleet." Clean white background for the text area. Educational, useful, highly pinnable content. Crisp, professional photos.*

