### 7. YOUTUBE (Thumbnail for Videos)

**Prompt 7A – Clickbait "Insane Transformation" Thumbnail (1280x720)**
> *High-energy YouTube thumbnail image. Extreme close-up of a vehicle wrap being peeled back to reveal the new shiny color underneath. The background is a blurred workshop. The lighting is dramatic and punchy with high contrast. No text in the image (you will add text in editing). The subject fills 80% of the frame. Bright colors, sharp details, intense focus on the peeling action. YouTube clickbait style.*

**Prompt 7B – "How It's Made" Thumbnail (1280x720)**
> *YouTube thumbnail featuring a large format printer in action, printing a massive colorful banner. The printer heads are visible, and ink droplets are frozen in motion (macro shot). The workshop lighting is blue and cool, creating a high-tech, industrial feel. The image is ultra-sharp. Focus on the technology and machinery. Appeals to people curious about the printing process.*

